311
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:01,280
ohľadom mňa.

312
00:19:09,335 --> 00:19:12,005
Ak nám osud dopraje, znovu sa stretneme.

313
00:19:38,660 --> 00:19:40,640
Zdravím, mladý pane.

314
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,880
Stoj!

315
00:19:57,060 --> 00:19:58,260
Si šťastný...

316
00:19:58,700 --> 00:19:59,900
